trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of all [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elements in a project.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av alle [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elementer i et prosjekt.

trans-unit.source: Adds a new [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element to the end of the project.
trans-unit.target: Legger til en ny [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elementet til slutten av prosjektet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""></xref> attribute of the new <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""> </xref> for den nye <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""> </xref> elementet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref> object representing the created `Target` element.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"> </xref> -objekt som representerer den opprettede `Target` elementet.

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref> to a compatible one-dimensional <xref:System.Array>, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: Overfører hele <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref> til en kompatibel endimensjonal <xref:System.Array>, med Start fra den angitte indeksen på Målmatrisen.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <xref:System.Array> that is the destination of the elements copied from <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den endimensjonal <xref:System.Array>som er målet for elementene kopieres fra <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref>.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Array> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Array>må ha nullbasert indeksering.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in `array` at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: Den nullbaserte indeksen i `array` som kopiering begynner.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating the number of <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref> objects in the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir antall <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"> </xref> objekter i den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> object in the collection represents a element in the project.
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>objektet i samlingen representerer et element i prosjektet.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>

trans-unit.source: An integer value representing the number of <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref> objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En heltallsverdi som representerer antall <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"> </xref> objekter i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref> exists in the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om den angitte <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"> </xref> finnes i den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""></xref> attribute of the Target element to search for.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""> </xref> for målelement til å søke etter.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the `Target` element exists; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den `Target` element finnes; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets an enumerator that iterates through the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter en opplisting som går gjennom den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This method allows the caller to use the `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) to iterate through the individual <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> objects in the <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kan oppkalleren å bruke den `foreach` -setningen for språket C# (`for each` i [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) å gå gjennom de individuelle <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>objekter i <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection>.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection> </xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> for the entire <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>for hele <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref>.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether access to the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref> is synchronized (thread safe).
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om tilgang til den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref> er synkronisert (tråden trygt).

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if access to the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref> is synchronized (thread safe); otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis tilgang til den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref> er synkronisert (tråden trygt); ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the specified <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"></xref> object in the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter den angitte <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target"> </xref> objekt i den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> object represents a `Target` element in the project.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>objekt representerer en `Target` elementet i prosjektet.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target>

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""></xref> attribute of the Target element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""> </xref> attributtet i mål-element i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The object that contains the property value specified by index.
trans-unit.target: Den objekt som inneholder den egenskapsverdien som er angitt av index .

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) element from the project.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner det angitte [Target](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elementet fra prosjektet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""></xref> attribute of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""></xref> element to remove.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Name" name="Name" href=""> </xref> for den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Target" name="Target" href=""> </xref> elementet til å fjerne.

trans-unit.source: Gets an object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter et objekt som kan brukes til å synkronisere tilgang til den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: An object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection"></xref>.
